verse.lines:
You've got My Word on it,
 Every verse, every line;
 Hold fast to the promises,
 And everything will work out fine;
 No matter what your pain or hurt in life,
 I will be there to bear your strife;
 You've got My Word on it,
 My Word Divine.

Now there's a promise of the rapture,
 You see, I've got it all arranged;
 The Holy Ghost is gonna lead you,
 Through that body change;
 So for now just hold on strong,
 I'll be with you all the way;
 Rest assured it won't be long,
'Till you see the glorious day.
